557
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:40,150
If you don't want to go,

558
00:21:40,150 --> 00:21:41,600
why do you call me?

559
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:44,320
I just want to discuss with you.

560
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:46,870
The school will cover the travel expenses.

561
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:47,730
Don't worry about it.

562
00:21:47,730 --> 00:21:48,550
I'll send you money.

563
00:21:48,550 --> 00:21:49,430
You must go.

564
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:51,270
Confidently. Xiaowa.

565
00:21:51,430 --> 00:21:53,550
No need, brother. I have money.

566
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:55,420
I'm hanging up. I'm going to work.

567
00:21:58,180 --> 00:22:00,840
My little brother is about to win another award.

568
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:06,540
You know this place?

569
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:08,390
I haven't been here many times.

570
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:09,860
I'm not bragging,

571
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:11,080
but normally,

572
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:12,990
I have a wide range of interests,

573
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:15,850
including culinary arts, medicine, plants and animals,

574
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:17,200
archaeology, history,

575
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:18,620
poetry and literature.

576
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:21,220
I'm practically an expert

577
00:22:21,320 --> 00:22:23,510
in astronomy and geography.

578
00:22:24,530 --> 00:22:26,030
Yaya's interest in this area was nurtured by me.

579
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:26,660
I even bought him

580
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:27,860
his first telescope.

